Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt's not so... bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was kind of\Na weird name to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] And if any boys so\Nmuch as look at Miss Yoko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,--the wrong way...\N--[YU] Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] ...they'll have\Nto answer to my trusty bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NLook, there it is! The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] It's not really summer\Nuntil you go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] This was so\Nworth waking up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never taken a\Ntrain to the beach before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes it feel more like we're\Non an adventure or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You usually get here by limo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Or helicopter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What'll we do\Nonce we're there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Lie on the beach and\Nlook up at the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Make sandcastles and\Ncatch up on some reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat ice cream and watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWell, ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it's time\Nfor us to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] It's summer.\NSummer means the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,The ocean means a good\Nold fashioned beach hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So I present to you,\NSecret Garden, beach hut style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Have a bite of paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we traveled\Nall this way just to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,At least the\Nscenery's nicer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NWe should be pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Mitsugu, I was\Nable to get a prime location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOf course it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHe does "live to serve," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:27.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NWe're still setting things up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,but it should be ready\Nto open tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAwesome. Can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI'm curious, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you going to call\Nit now that it's out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.51,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's not really\Na garden anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Secret Garden: Beach-Hut Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA]\NWell... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI'm not so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have a great ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's\Na good name, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Be nice or it's back\Nto the bread crust diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, well... It's not so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, to be totally honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was kind of\Na weird name to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It is a classic story,\Nand I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,you've never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's\Nwhat you're going for,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little Shop of Horrors{\i0}\Nmight be more appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe {\i1}Little Women{\i0} .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we all please move on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,We were only\Ntrying to be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need\Nyour help, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You can forget about\Nchanging her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,because she's as\Nstubborn as she is tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're not a fan\Nof the name either?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's always seemed\Nstrange to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I never got what a garden\Nhad to do with cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We're opening the beach hut\Nversion of Secret Garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,and that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NUm... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I do still have one question,\Nif you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You keep saying "beach hut."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] You've never\Nheard of a beach hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NLet's be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not her fault she\Ndoesn't know these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] The rich are oblivious\Nto the world around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:57.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that I've never\Nheard of a beach hut before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I simply don't know\Nwhat one is exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,or how it's supposed to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's up to you to tell me\Nprecisely what a beach hut is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Using interpretive dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I am waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I am wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't form a\Npicture in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,How can I work at a\Nplace I don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NSand! I am the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI'm totally lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Just when you thought\Nshe couldn't get weirder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:46.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, um, we came\Nall the way out here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,to work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,but I was kind of looking\Nforward to the extra money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll just\Ndo my best, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Now that that's\Nsettled, let's get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYeah, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI brought some cute outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta tell ya, I'm not\Ntotally the biggest fan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:05.03,Main,,0,0,0,,of this stupid beach\Nhut idea of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's\Nso great about sunburns
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,and sand in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And if any boys so much\Nas look at Miss Yoko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,the wrong way, they'll have to\Nanswer to my trusty bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Will they?\NI'm sure they're terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYum! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's delicious! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like a party in my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Mmm! I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Should I try the melon\Nor the orange next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to decide.\NI want them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that\Ngirl's eating over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6A]\NWhatever it is, I want some!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! Could she\Nbe any more obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You should have let me\Nbe the fake customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I would've done a better\Njob than that ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I appreciate her enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] There are bound to\Nbe a bunch of handsy boys
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,flocking to Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need\Nall the help I can get
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,keeping them at a safe distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I don't think\Nthat's gonna be an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat was a pretty big sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't\Nexactly look like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No. I was thinking more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NSummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Splashing under the bright sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Three girls reveling in\Ntheir youthful bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] The sweet lure\Nof unblemished flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Rivaled only by the sweetness\Nof the shop's wares.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Secret Garden, beach hut-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Open this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Come and join the fun! Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,As if I would let you\Nflaunt her body like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And that whole\Ndisguise bit at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,was just plain embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you at least wear\Na cute little tank top
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,or shorts, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] And wind up with\Nfunny-looking tan lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone needs to\Ncompensate for the lack of skin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko is showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama, I'm changing your\Nuniform to a bikini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] If it's so important,\Nchange your own outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] You keep calling\Nthis place a beach hut,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,but it feels more\Nlike a fancy café.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Beach-hut inspired,\Nwith a more elevated cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Gelato, frappes, and\Nother fancy desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat about ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,And curry! And fried noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] That would be silly.\NWe're a dessert shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I eat fried noodles\Nfor dessert all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NYou would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Come to Secret Garden:\NBeach-Hut Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Open today!\NSecret Garden: Beach-Hut Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Secret Garden:\NBeach-Hut Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Drop on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The name's just too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No wonder people\Naren't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should try\Na different spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NYoko! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS shriek]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NYoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard you were\Nworking at a beach hut,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to show my support,\Nso I came as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take one of\Neverything, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know if\Nyou want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.05,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a big menu and it's\Nall frozen desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NOh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno if I could eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI can help you with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not kidding.\NShe eats like a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there such thing as\Na permanent brain freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not take a break?\NYou don't have to finish it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You made this with\Nyour own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.78,Main,,0,0,0,,and I won't let all your\Nhard work go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry it took a little\Nlonger than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But I thought Yoko was\Nmaking all the desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Messing with a little kid\Nlike that is so immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NI dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, there are worse\Nthings than being immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Like being tiny and\Nevil, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Or like being a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Or an obsessive\Ncreep with no life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Since today was\Nonly our soft opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I decided to close\Nthe shop early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for\Nyour hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I was happy with our sales,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.11,Main,,0,0,0,,especially considering\Nit was just a half-day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Working on the beach is harder\Nthan I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so hot, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Stylish turtleneck, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I thought it would be\Nnice to celebrate our success
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and keep our spirits\Nhigh for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,How does a barbecue\Nsound to everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NSure, count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You think that's the\Nbest idea at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NI'm a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This much food is\Nnothing to me. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially if you're the one\Ndoing the cooking this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody!\NIt's time to eat! Who's hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I think a little barbecue\Nwill brighten your mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that, ladies?\NDid you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If my cooking isn't to\Nyour liking, Master Yu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to whip\Nsomething else up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU] No, don't bother.\NI'll just sit this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,One more bite and I'd\Nprobably puke, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I say\Nbring on the meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] There's nothing\Nbetter than a good meal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,after working all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NMm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, Yamaji! Load me\Nup with some more veggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,meat, meat, meat, meat,\Nmeat, meat, and fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So much for today's profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NTeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're grilling?\NThat looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured it must be hard\Nwork getting a new business
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd come\Nand offer to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,We're done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That was nice of her to come\Nand check in on us, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Would you like Mitsugu\Nto put together a plate for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NThat would be great. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,The little cutie's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NHi again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not eating anything?\NThat's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,A young boy like you\Nneeds plenty of food
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,to keep your strength up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! You wait here.\NI'll make some for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[stomach gurgling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Thanks.\NThat sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I think this might\Nbe what breaks him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Eh, it's just\Na little barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] It's actually better\Nto eat meat raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You get more vitamins that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NUgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] I'll call an ambulance\Nand have them on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Come and cool off at\NSecret Garden: Beach-Hut Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOne mango frappé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I get you anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Our last day of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we\Nwere gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] It was tough,\Nbut we survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] It sucks that\Nwe didn't get to relax
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,while we were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't come for a vacation.\NWe came to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It would've been a lot\Nharder without you two here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,so thanks for letting\Nme drag you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No problem.\NGlad we could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWow, Futaba. You sure are tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI was gonna go with "burned."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's summer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NSo what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer means curry, right?\NAnd now I kinda look like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] You say that\Nlike it's a good thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Anyway, I've got\Na farmer's tan now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,and I want to even it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Since we won't\Nbe working tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I say we go hang out\Non the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,We haven't been swimming\Neven once since we came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,and that's just plain\Nunacceptable if you ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm pretty much\Ndone with my homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'm ready to chill\Nfor the rest of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, homework?\NWhat is this mysterious word?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've\Nheard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd have to pay\Nattention in class
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,to be familiar\Nwith that concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Since you'll be enjoying\Nyour day off tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,why don't I make\Nlunch as a thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,for all your hard work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Is there anything\Nin particular you'd like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NBarbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] We already had that\Nthe first day we were out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] What's the\Nbeach without barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,They're a classic pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Well, there's\Nthe sand and the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NFine, then curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Not after that\Ncomparison you made earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can come up with\Nsomething everybody will like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NAw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just focus on\Nenjoying the ocean tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet I can catch me\Na fat fish or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Tomorrow is\Ngonna be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ocean, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Shark can be tricky,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,but if it's fresh and\Nyou've got a hot grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You're crazy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NNo fair! Go away, shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,This really is too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It would have been so much\Nnicer if it was a dolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,instead of a shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYep, sure would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NHey, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not working\Nanymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,So does that mean you\Ncan have a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We were hoping to,\Nbut the beach is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Shark sighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NNo problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU] I can get us\Ninto the hotel pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,How 'bout it? Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIf you're sure it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,What about lunch?\NCan we barbecue there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You look like you've\Nalready been barbecued.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HAYAMA, YOKO] Wow!\N--[FUTABA] Wow! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAnd so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Thanks for bringing us,\NYu. This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YU] Not the ocean,\Nbut it's still nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NThis'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since we've\Ngone swimming together, Teru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUm, awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember, no running or\Ndiving in the shallow end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's your floatie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, suddenly I'm\Nnot so jealous anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Does anybody\Nknow where Sonobe is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I guess the cooking's\Ntaking longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she'd meet\Nus by lunch, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay, last one in the\Npool's a rotten egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NFutaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SAKURA]\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, suddenly\NI don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,She kinda has that\Neffect on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,My parents took me\Nhere on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, hunk! Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I think the damage was more\Npsychological than physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope it's nothing\Nserious, poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWait, where's Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't go with him, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,He's been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time you see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,give 'em a kiss on the\Ncheek or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I guess I owe\Nhim that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's a big,\Nbeautiful pool waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NRight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIn honor of our fallen warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NWoohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you believe\Nhow awesome this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hotel pools are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you stop the\Nrunning and squealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] If you stop\Nbeing a party pooper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,and have a little fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, you are dressed like\Nyou're ready for a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This? It's just something\NI had laying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, thanks for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty cool that you\Nwere able to score tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NSomeone gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHayama's older sister Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] But why would she\Ngive them to you of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It was kinda random.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[bell ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,How am I gonna\Ncarry all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I can help if you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You helped Hayama's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] Yep, and then she\Ngave me some tickets she'd won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] How am I\Nsupposed to enjoy myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,knowing that's how you got them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Well at least it isn't like\Nthe evil one herself is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.\NThat's Hayama over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like they're\Nhaving a lotta fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NMaybe we should say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NNot a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Look what I found down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,In case I ever go\Ndeep sea fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] How is that\Nlike deep sea fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And, you know,\Nyou might get in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.67,Main,,0,0,0,,if the hotel people\Nsee you doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that wouldn't be so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt's your friend, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You always show up\Nwherever I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't\Nlike you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd rather go out with\Na rabid dog than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Hey! You're the nice\Ngirl who helped me before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks again for the tickets!\NThis place rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a freakin' party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] I don't think you've\Nmentioned this friend
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,before, Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Nishiyama. I'd consider\Nher more of a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.86,Main,,0,0,0,,How great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you're here too, why\Ndon't we all hang out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... No! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,There're already some\Nfriends here I have to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got other friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NCome on, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I can go\Nfinish my sandcastle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to take a\Ndip in the pool real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] No, I don't.\NAnd you should know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThat explains the floatie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:57.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI never would've guessed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Swimming's a pretty\Nimportant skill to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, what if you're\Non a boat and it sinks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the\Nocean or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let us help you\Nwork on your swimming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You never know when\Nit might come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,When do you think it\Nmight come in handy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,They're so different,\Nyet so similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Get back in there\Nand keep on trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll get better if\Nyou give it some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNo, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I just don't\Nunderstand why anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,would hate the water so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NMainly because it can kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I've lasted this long not\Nknowing how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,And I really don't see\Nany particular reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,to change that now,\Nbecause I think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine\Njust the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Come on! We'll go\Npractice in the kiddie pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NGood luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NI know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NHey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Hope you're hungry.\NI come bearing lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never been so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You took a lot\Nlonger than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI know, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I was working with\Nsome new ingredients,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,so I needed a little extra time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you are.\NI hope you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThis is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] It was my first\Ntime too, and I gotta say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,it was pretty exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Y'know... you guys\Naren't looking so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What can I say?\NIt was a pretty wild ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,And harder than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But we were able to get\Nhold of a rare ingredient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,so it was worth it in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by\Na rare ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] Let's just say\NI don't think that shark
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,will be bothering us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I would still skip\Nthe swimming, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Tons of jellyfish out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'm still confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yummy!\N--Did you really just eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I got a fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,That's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Being in the sun all day\Ncan really wear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You can use me as\Na pillow if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.\NThat's what big sisters are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer,\Nbut I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And what about you?\NWant a shoulder to lean on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I would feel silly sleeping\Nin public like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, just one more bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]\NI'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWas she sleep talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,She's probably having a feast\Nin her dream right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,If I go to sleep, will I get\Nto dream about having a feast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThat's not really how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep, Yoko.\NClose your eyes and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll work\Nif you're trying that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Sleep's kinda more\Nabout relaxing, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYou must sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUm, Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:16.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You must sleep now.\NEyes closed. Deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sleep. Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI can't eat another bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But I can. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSeriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I cannot.\NI cannot eat anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I will take the rest to-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot?\N[whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.40,0:24:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NA nightmare.
